{"type": "article", "id": 15862, "title": "产生错觉的书架", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-10T07:51:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021355489QJCKViWY53jecTG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t黎巴嫩设计师 Charles Kalpakian 酷爱玩弄错觉艺术，推出了一款名叫“rocky”的书柜，主要由长方形和菱形表面组成。从不同角度看过去，反光面都是不同的，使书柜呈现出不同的立体样式，令人对凹凸产生错觉，有未来感。部件全部通过 3D 打印制作，有蓝、黑、银灰三种颜色。<a href=\"http://www.lachance.fr/fr/product/details/16/Rocky\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143149AtbGfscxoERWvzBC.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"890\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.08801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143149xukEIimG5f4OTzbH.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"870\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.06356968\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143150foAh8OLrCjgMXWqB.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"614\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143151PcXFIExlktzhO8RY.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"458\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}